remake (1:0.5.3-166) lucid; urgency=low

  * Changed mechanism for testing whether cache variables have already
    been initialized (now using an internal cache flag instead of
    ${CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX_INITIALIZED_TO_DEFAULT})
  * New features:
    + Added keyword arguments EXTRA_C_FLAGS, EXTRA_CXX_FLAGS, and
      EXTRA_SHARED_LINKER_FLAGS to remake_project(), allowing the
      project maintainer to "inject" project-specific build settings to
      CMake's standard cache variable
  * Increased patch version

 -- Ralf Kaestner <ralf.kaestner@gmail.com>  Wed, 10 Apr 2013 09:10:00 +0100

