  * Fixed bug in remake_pack_deb() that prevented correct matching of package
    dependencies on launchpad build systems

 -- Ralf Kaestner <ralf.kaestner@gmail.com>  Fri, 23 Mar 2013 19:20:00 +0100

remake (1:0.5.1-157) lucid; urgency=low

  * New features
    + Added VERBATIM option to remake_list()
    + Added VERSION argument to remake_pack_binary() and remake_pack_source()
  * Changes and bugfixes
    + remake_pack_deb() now uses = instead of >= to indicate an exact
      match in a dependency to another package in the same project
    + Fixed bug in remake_distribute_deb() that caused unmet dependencies
      when installing distributed binary packages (control file now contains
      dependencies with the distribution names appended to the version)
    + Changed remake_distribute_deb() such that, when detecting a release
      build, the control file is updated with the matched package
      dependencies of the build system

 -- Ralf Kaestner <ralf.kaestner@gmail.com>  Fri, 23 Mar 2013 13:07:00 +0100

